ygData.messageBody:
Tarew's Aquatic Ayre can only be found in High Hold.
As far as it being useful, I believe the place is called Kerr Keep. Totally
underwater (to get there at least). I've also heard that there is something
interesting lying deep in Lake Rathetear...

Good Journey,

Sineras Silverlyre (Cazic-Thule)
